    <li>story(uses=1,priority=-10)->None could surpass [founderName]'s understanding of [memeConcept], and [founder_pronoun] was appointed the first [leaderTitle] of the [memberNamePlural].</li>
    <li>story(uses=1,priority=-10)->[founderName] carried a [relic0_thingDef_label] named [relic0_name] with [founder_objective] everywhere to remind people to live a [memeAdjective] life.</li>
